WHEREAS, the Landlord agrees to let, and the Tenant agrees to take on rent the premises described below:

1. PROPERTY DESCRIPTION:

The Landlord hereby agrees to rent out the residential property located at:
Address: Flat No. 5C, Sunshine Apartments, Whitefield,
City: Bangalore,
State: Karnataka,
PIN: 560066.

2. TERM:

The rental term shall begin on 1st November, 2024 and continue for a period of 11 months, unless terminated earlier in accordance with this Agreement.

3. RENT:

The monthly rent for the above property is INR 25,000 (Rupees Twenty-Five Thousand only) payable in advance on or before the 5th day of each month.

The payment shall be made via Bank Transfer to the following account:
Bank Name: HDFC Bank,
Account Number: 1234567890,
IFSC Code: HDFC0001234.

4. SECURITY DEPOSIT:

The Tenant agrees to pay a security deposit of INR 75,000 (Rupees Seventy-Five Thousand only), refundable upon the termination of the lease, subject to any deductions for damages beyond normal wear and tear.

5. MAINTENANCE AND UTILITIES:

The Tenant shall be responsible for maintaining the interior of the property in good condition.
The Landlord shall be responsible for major repairs related to the structure of the building and utilities such as water and electricity supply.
All utility bills such as electricity, water, gas, etc., will be paid by the Tenant.
6. RESTRICTIONS:

The Tenant shall not sub-let the property without the prior written consent of the Landlord.
No illegal activities or hazardous materials are allowed on the premises.
Any structural alterations are prohibited without the prior consent of the Landlord.
7. TERMINATION:

This agreement can be terminated by either party with a prior notice of 2 months. In the event of early termination by the Tenant, the security deposit may be forfeited unless otherwise agreed by the Landlord.

8. GOVERNING LAW:

This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India, and any disputes arising hereunder shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts in Bangalore.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties hereto have executed this House Rental Agreement on the date set forth above.

Signature of Landlord: Ravi Kumar
Signature of Tenant: Anjali Sharma

